Localization.Name: Ambrus Suit
Localization.Description: MuyMuy's Ambrus suit was expertly crafted by artisans on Saisei from natural brocade silk and worsted ma'xy.un wool. Featuring bold coloration and a relaxed fit, it lets the wearer maintain comfort without sacrificing style.
